# Douyin 去广告
# 重点广告接口（精准拦截）
URL-REGEX,^https?:\/\/.*\/v1\/(ad|ads|advert|log)\/
URL-REGEX,^https?:\/\/.*\/api\/ad\/
URL-REGEX,^https?:\/\/.*\/api\/ad\/v\d\/
URL-REGEX,^https?:\/\/.*\/service\/2\/app_log\/
URL-REGEX,^https?:\/\/.*\/service\/2\/log\/

DOMAIN-SUFFIX,fp.tongdun.net
